'''水牛地雷防護車'''（Buffalo mine protected vehicle）是由Force Protection參考[[南非|南非]]的[[卡斯皮裝甲車|卡斯皮地雷防護車]]（Casspir）開發而成<ref>[http://www.defensetech.org/archives/001233.html Defense Tech: More On Warlock'S Tricks<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080409144931/http://www.defensetech.org/archives/001233.html |date=2008-04-09 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Buffalo helps protect from bullets, blasts |url=http://www.dix.army.mil/PAO/Post04/post111904/bullets.htm |publisher=[[美國國防部|美國國防部]] |date=2004-09-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060206230857/http://www.dix.army.mil/PAO/Post04/post111904/bullets.htm |archivedate=2006-02-06 }}</ref>，至2008年6月6日，[[美軍|美軍]]已裝備二百架<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.upi.com/Security_Industry/2008/06/06/200th_Buffalo_MRAP_delivered_to_military/UPI-15781212771850/ |title=200th Buffalo MRAP delivered to military - UPI.com<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2008-08-23 |archive-date=2008-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080609082315/http://www.upi.com/Security_Industry/2008/06/06/200th_Buffalo_MRAP_delivered_to_military/UPI-15781212771850/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
[[File:Buffalo_IED.jpg|thumb]]攻擊後的水牛（加裝了鳥籠式裝甲），車體仍保持完整]]
==設計==
[[卡斯皮裝甲車|卡斯皮地雷防護車]]原為四輪設計，而水牛地雷防護車則改為六輪，車頭具有大型遙控工程臂以用於處理爆炸品。水牛採用[[V型車殼|V型車殼]]，若車底有[[地雷|地雷]]或[[IED|IED]]爆炸時能將衝擊波分散，有效保護車內人員免受嚴重傷害<ref>{{cite web | title = Combat engineers comb streets of Iraq for IEDs | url = http://www.ngb.army.mil/news/story.asp?id=1660 | publisher = [[美國國防部|美國國防部]] | date = 2005-07-08 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20060203124922/http://www.ngb.army.mil/news/story.asp?id=1660 | archivedate = 2006-02-03 }}</ref>。在[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]及[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]服役的水牛更加裝[[鳥籠式裝甲|鳥籠式裝甲]]以防護[[RPG-7|RPG-7]]的攻擊<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.defenseindustrydaily.com/baes-lrod-cage-armor-03473 |title=BAE’s LROD Cage Armor - Defense Industry Daily<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2008-08-23 |archive-date=2012-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120129065912/http://www.defenseindustrydaily.com/baes-lrod-cage-armor-03473/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

